There are two hidden things in this map, one however would be a major 
waste of time and i really dont know way i
left it there. The bots for both sides work. They can be pretty stupid 
sometimes, but it was my first time nav
mesh editing so there really isnt much i can do about that. this is a 
rather simple map that is easy to run and
great practice for getting headshots. There is a way out to but no mans 
land is pretty dangerous and so is trying
to get into the other bunker, unless someone is afk.
